summary: Adds a skeleton to the Drunken Huntsman.
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]http://162.243.85.154/netfu/tmp28000/coollogo_com-56191629.png[/img]
[img]http://fc01.deviantart.net/fs70/f/2011/208/a/b/divider_by_canzeda-d41w92p.png[/img]

Features:

• Adds a skeleton to the Drunken Huntsman in Whiterun.
• Its name is Skellie and its very old and grumpy. (If you stand near it, it'll say stuff).

You can't talk to Skellie, sorry. It can only talk to you.


[img]http://fc01.deviantart.net/fs70/f/2011/208/a/b/divider_by_canzeda-d41w92p.png[/img]
FAQ

Q: What does this mod do?
A: This mod adds a skeleton to the Drunken Huntsman.

Q: Where is Skellie located?
A: In the Drunken Huntsman in Whiterun.

Q: Skellie isn't talking to me.
A: It probably doesn't like your company.

Enjoy![/center]
author: Mure
